categories.", "type": "text"}]}, {"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"text": "The company is also supported by a powerhouse Board of Advisors with global expertise in healthcare, education, AI, design, and venture capital including Ibrahim Al Hudhaif, Dr. Halim Choueiry, Hayssam Ibrahim, Hassan Ballout, and Fran Owens all united by one shared belief: Moonshot or Nothing", "type": "text"}]}, {"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"text": "Why Now?", "type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}]}]}, {"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"text": "Because there’s never been a better or more urgent time.", "type": "text"}]}, {"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"text": "AI has lowered the barrier to execution. You no longer need a massive team to launch a product. But while the ‘", "type": "text"}, {"text": "how’", "type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "italic"}]}, {"text": " of building has gotten easier, the '", "type": "text"}, {"text": "what'", "type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "italic"}]}, {"text": " and '", "type": "text"}, {"text": "why'", "type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "italic"}]}, {"text": " have become exponentially more important.", "type": "text"}]}, {"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"text": "In an era of automation and sameness, originality is the new unfair advantage. Whole-brain and creative thinking have become the most valuable assets and Obsession believes the time to act on them is now before the window closes.", "type": "text"}]}, {"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"text": "Who It’s For", "type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}]}]}, {"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"text": "The Moonshot Challenge is built for founders with disruptive ideas too bold for the average business lens, investors or family offices exploring future-defining ventures, corporate leaders seeking to embed risk-taking and long-term thinking into their culture, as well as family offices ready to incubate ventures with purpose and edge and entrepreneurs pivoting from traditional businesses to original plays.", "type": "text"}, {"type": "hardBreak"}, {"text": "If your idea doesn’t quite “fit” what’s expected, that may be the best sign it’s worth building.", "type": "text"}]}, {"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"text": "What’s Next?", "type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}]}]}, {"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"text": "The Moonshot Challenge is now live. Obsession is selectively onboarding new projects starting this summer.", "type": "text"}]}, {"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"text": "To explore if your idea is a fit, visit", "type": "text"}, {"text": " itsobsession.com/the-moonshot-challenge", "type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "link", "attrs": {"rel": "nofollow", "href": "https://itsobsession.com/the-moonshot-challenge", "target": "_blank"}}]}]}]}}	\N	2025-10-09 19:54:47.624+00	2025-10-28 12:22:07.74684+00	\N	\N	https://itsobsession.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/3245353.webp	\N	\N	0	{"likes": 0, "views": 0, "comments": 0}	\N	\N	obsession-launches-the-moonshot-challenge	\N	{}	f	\N	\N	{}	\N	\N	\N	{}	\N	\N	\N	\N	0	0	\N
