7f877041-792d-4f22-98a6-2e03c8ac90c1	Unlock Success: Mastering Financial Risk for Business Leaders  | Essential Tips & Tools!	Video	\N	ADSMEHub	Published	2025-11-18 00:00:00+00	\N	In the world of business, navigating financial landscapes can be daunting, especially when dealing with big players like banks and financing companies. Ever wished you could speak their language and avoid awkward meetings? The key is financial literacy!\n\nJoin us in this engaging video where we debunk the myth that financial management is dull and purely about crunching numbers. It's not rocket science; it's a fascinating journey of uncovering what has happened, much like a forensic scientist. Understanding the vocabulary, tools, and concepts is the key to success.\n\nWithout financial literacy, you risk poor credit, bankruptcy, and other debt burdens – a nightmare for any business leader. Let's start with the basics.\n\nFeeling overwhelmed? Don't worry! See financial literacy as a guide to making better decisions, increasing your company’s profitability, strength, and cash generation.\n	{}	https://tse4.mm.bing.net/th/id/OIP.AfU28xk1KTXoND0rem7gyAHaEK?rs=1&pid=ImgDetMain&o=7&rm=3	0	0	{"author_bio": null, "author_org": null, "author_name": "ADSMEHub", "author_title": null, "author_photo_url": null}	\N	2025-11-18 07:18:06.953482+00	2025-11-18 08:00:14.774182+00	\N	\N	https://tse4.mm.bing.net/th/id/OIP.AfU28xk1KTXoND0rem7gyAHaEK?rs=1&pid=ImgDetMain&o=7&rm=3	\N	\N	0	{"likes": 0, "views": 0, "comments": 0}	\N	\N	unlock-success-mastering-financial-risk-for-business-leaders-essential-tips-tools	\N	{}	f	https://kfmediaitems.blob.core.windows.net/mediaitems/video/1763449408980-unlock-success-mastering-financial-risk-for-business-leaders-essential-tips-tools-2.mp4	\N	{}	\N	\N	\N	{}	\N	\N	\N	\N	0	0	\N
