9578fbd5-b595-4793-a707-beabc4c348ea	Master Your Business Finances: Why Financial Management Matters | Learn the Game Plan!	Video	\N	ADSMEHub	Published	2025-11-18 08:09:04.901+00	\N	Did you know that a staggering 82% of new businesses collapse within 5 years for the same reason? Financial mismanagement! In this eye-opening video, uncover the hidden dangers lurking behind seemingly successful businesses. Learn why 70% of them remain oblivious to the impending disaster.\n\nDiscover the strategic game plan every business needs for financial success. Dive into the roles of the Chief Financial Officer (CFO), financial managers, and accountants with our detailed infographic. But what if you're just starting? Don't worry! Explore alternatives like part-time CFOs, CFO-as-a-service, and AI Finance software that leverage core financial management tools.\n\nUnravel the mysteries of key financial statements - the income statement, cash flow statement, and balance sheet. Each tells a unique story about your company's financial health and performance. Want to delve deeper? Check out our other infographic for an in-depth exploration.\n\nHungry for more financial wisdom? Stay tuned for our next video on mastering financial risk because, in business, it's not just about making money; it's about keeping it! Subscribe now and level up your financial game.	{}	https://tse4.mm.bing.net/th/id/OIP.XgfSEVpJvDCPCLyKrMMgUQHaEK?rs=1&pid=ImgDetMain&o=7&rm=3	0	0	{"author_bio": null, "author_org": null, "author_name": "ADSMEHub", "author_title": null, "author_photo_url": null}	\N	2025-11-12 13:43:27.089799+00	2025-11-18 08:09:06.353564+00	\N	\N	https://tse4.mm.bing.net/th/id/OIP.XgfSEVpJvDCPCLyKrMMgUQHaEK?rs=1&pid=ImgDetMain&o=7&rm=3	\N	\N	0	{"likes": 0, "views": 0, "comments": 0}	\N	\N	master-your-business-finances-why-financial-management-matters-learn-the-game-plan	\N	{}	f	https://kfmediaitems.blob.core.windows.net/mediaitems/video/1762953728885-master-your-business-finances-why-financial-mana